articles.title: Required Documents (EU/Schengen)
articles.content:
To travel within the Schengen area, you generally need a valid ID card or Passport. 

Check expiration dates before traveling.

articles.title: Vignette Rules: Bulgaria
articles.content:
Driving on national roads in Bulgaria requires a valid Vignette (BGTOLL). 

You can buy it online or at the border.

articles.title: Speed Limits: Greece
articles.content:
Standard speed limits in Greece:
- Highway: 130 km/h
- Rural roads: 90 km/h
- City: 50 km/h
